'''Lacus Odii''' ([[Latin]] for "Lake of Hate") is a small [[lunar mare]] in the [[Terra Nivium]] region on the [[Moon]]. It is located at 19.0° N, 7.0° E and is 70&nbsp;km in diameter.

{{Lunar maria}}

[[Category:Maria on the Moon|Odii]]

