ons)|Azer]] |PageNumber=22–23 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Azer warrior, azer foot soldier, azer rager, azer taskmaster, azer beastlord |Description=Resembles a dwarf with brass-colored skin, and hair and beard of flames }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Balhannoth]] |PageNumber=24 |OtherAppearances= |Variants= |Description=Large worm-like aberration with tentacles }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Banshrae]] |PageNumber=25 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Banshrae dartswarmer, banshrae warrior |Description=Humanoids with insect-like features }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Basilisk (Dungeons & Dragons)|Basilisk]] |PageNumber=26 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Venom-eye basilisk, stone-eye basilisk |Description=Large six (sometimes eight)-legged lizard }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Bat]] |PageNumber=27 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Shadowhunter bat, fire bat |Description=Large bat-like creatures }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Battlebriar]] |PageNumber=28 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Warthorn battlebriar, earthrage battlebriar |Description=Plant creatures resembling large frogs with claws and large teeth }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Bear]] |PageNumber=29 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Cave bear, dire bear |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Beetle]] |PageNumber=30 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Fire beetle, tangler beetle, rot scarab swarm |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Dinosaur (Dungeons & Dragons)|Behemoth]] |PageNumber=31 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Macetail behemoth, bloodspike behemoth |Description=Bloodspike behemoth resembles a large reptile similar in form to the [[Stegosaurus|Stegosaurus stenops]] and macetail behemoth resembles a large reptile similar in form to the [[Euoplocephalus|Euoplocephalus tutus]] }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Beholder (Dungeons & Dragons)|Beholder]] |PageNumber=32–33 |OtherAppearances= |Variants=Beholder eye of flame, beholder eye tyrant |Description=Resembles a floating orb of flesh with a large mouth, single central eye,