==WTC 21828 – Forgotten Realms Campaign Guide (2008)== Released in August 2008, this book details the [[Forgotten Realms]] campaign setting. It includes unique creatures, such as the zairtail, as well as a number of servants of the various groups and cults across the Realms. The table below is organized by the order the creatures first appear.
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-4924-3}}
