==WTC 21783 – Adventurer's Vault (2008)== This book, published in September 2008, details various weapons, armor, vehicles, mounts, and other magical items. All of the monsters found in this book are mounts and/or creatures summoned through the use of magic items. The table below is organized by the order the creatures first appear.
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-4978-6}}
