==239667200 – Monster Manual 2 (2009)== {{Expand section|date=July 2011}} {{ISBN|978-0-7869-5101-7}}
==253840000 – Monster Manual 3 (2010)== {{Expand section|date=July 2011}} {{ISBN|978-0-7869-5490-2}}
==253840000 – Dark Sun Creature Catalog (2010)== {{Expand section|date=July 2011}} {{ISBN|978-0-7869-5494-0}}
==244650000 – Monster Vault (2010)== A boxed set that includes a book with a revised and streamlined core listing of monsters for the Dungeons & Dragons [[Editions of Dungeons & Dragons#Dungeons & Dragons 4th edition|4th edition]] game, published in 2010 as part of the Essentials line. The book features an introduction on pages 4–11, the monster descriptions on pages 12–295, an appendix of animals on pages 296–304, a glossary on pages 305–312, and a list of the monsters in the book ranked by level on pages 313–319.
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-5631-9}}
