'''Yumurtalık Lagoon''' ({{lang-tr|Yumurtalık Lagünü}}) is a [[lagoon]] located in [[Adana Province]], southern Turkey. The area is a [[nature reserve]], a former [[List of national parks in Turkey|national park]], and is a [[List of Ramsar sites in Turkey|Ramsar site]].<ref name="mp"/><ref name="mn"/><ref name="ro"/>

